3G/4G/LTE Module
----------------

|Product| is equipped with a **mini-PCIe connector** that can connect to a 3G/4G/LTE module.
The customer will also need a SIM Card Holder and a 3G/4G/LTE antenna to ensure 3G/4G/LTE works on the |product|. SIM card does **NOT** support hot plug. **Power off** before inserting or removing SIM card.

.. rst-class:: text-center

    |sim_img|

    *SIM Card Direction*

.. rst-class:: text-center

    |lte_img|

    *3G/4G/LTE Module*

.. attention::

    The product does not come shipped with the 3G/4G/LTE module by default. If you need to use 3G/4G/LTE, you can contact us when placing an order, we can install the necessary hardware for you.

:pagebreak:`True`
